  "root_text": {
    "iti35:0.1": "Itivuttaka 35 ",
    "iti35:0.2": "Dukanipāta ",
    "iti35:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti35:0.4": "Paṭhamajananakuhanasutta ",
    "iti35:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti35:2.1": "“Nayidaṁ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṁ vussati janakuhanatthaṁ, na janalapanatthaṁ, na lābhasakkārasilokānisaṁsatthaṁ, na ‘iti maṁ jano jānātū’ti. ",
    "iti35:2.2": "Atha kho idaṁ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṁ vussati saṁvaratthañceva pahānatthañcā”ti. ",
    "iti35:2.3": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti35:2.4": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti35:3.1": "“Saṁvaratthaṁ pahānatthaṁ, ",
    "iti35:3.2": "brahmacariyaṁ anītihaṁ; ",
    "iti35:3.3": "Adesayi so bhagavā, ",
    "iti35:3.4": "nibbānogadhagāminaṁ. ",
    "iti35:4.1": "Esa maggo mahattehi, ",
    "iti35:4.2": "anuyāto mahesibhi; ",
    "iti35:4.3": "Ye ye taṁ paṭipajjanti, ",
    "iti35:4.4": "yathā buddhena desitaṁ; ",
    "iti35:4.5": "Dukkhassantaṁ karissanti, ",
    "iti35:4.6": "satthusāsanakārino”ti. ",
    "iti35:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti35:5.2": "Aṭṭhamaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti35:0.1": "So It Was Said 35 ",
    "iti35:0.2": "The Book of the Twos ",
    "iti35:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti35:0.4": "Fawning and Flattery ",
    "iti35:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti35:2.1": "“Mendicants, this spiritual life is not lived for the sake of fawning or flattering people, nor for the benefit of possessions, honor, or popularity, nor thinking, ‘So let people know about me!’ ",
    "iti35:2.2": "This spiritual life is lived for the sake of restraint and giving up.” ",
    "iti35:2.3": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti35:2.4": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti35:3.1": "“The Buddha taught the spiritual life ",
    "iti35:3.2": "not because of tradition, ",
    "iti35:3.3": "but for the sake of restraint and giving up, ",
    "iti35:3.4": "and because it culminates in extinguishment. ",
    "iti35:4.1": "This is the path followed by the great souls, ",
    "iti35:4.2": "the great seers. ",
    "iti35:4.3": "Those who practice it ",
    "iti35:4.4": "as it was taught by the Buddha ",
    "iti35:4.5": "doing the teacher’s bidding, ",
    "iti35:4.6": "make an end of suffering.” ",
    "iti35:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
